titles.title: A resolution honoring Gonzaga University on its 125th anniversary.
A resolution honoring Gonzaga University on its 125th anniversary.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Honors Gonzaga University, located in Spokane, Washington, on its 125th anniversary.
Applauds Gonzaga University for its commitment to its students and for instilling in them the importance of service to others and civic engagement.
Congratulates its students, staff, faculty, alumni, and supporters for their many contributions in the United States and abroad.
